<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="111">Lepanthes oro-lojaensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was collected, in El Oro Province 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="111">A</emphasis>
natural vegetation remnants 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="111">B</emphasis>
areas where 
